column2: SELECT TOP # p.objid, p.ra AS ra, p.dec AS dec,  p.psfMag_g AS mag_g, p.psfMag_r AS mag_r, p.psfMag_i AS mag_i, p.petroR5#_r AS r_e, p.expAB_r AS b_a, s.z AS z, (# + #*(p.psfMag_g - p.psfMag_i)     - #*(p.psfMag_i - #*(log1#(s.z*#/#/#) + #))     ) as m_star FROM PhotoObj AS p    JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid  WHERE      ((p.type = #) -- galaxy     AND (p.b > # OR p.b < #)      AND (p.dec < #)     AND (s.z > #))
